Subject: Update on Your Recent Inquiry/Claim

Dear [Customer's Name],

I hope this message finds you well. I am writing to provide you with an update regarding your recent inquiry/claim with us.

After a thorough investigation, we have reached a conclusion and would like to inform you of the results and any necessary adjustments that will be made.

[Provide specific details about the inquiry/claim, the investigation results, and any adjustments or actions that will be taken.]

We understand the importance of this matter to you and are committed to ensuring your satisfaction. If you have any further questions or require additional assistance, please do not hesitate to contact us at [contact information].

Thank you for your patience and understanding.

Best regards,

[Your Full Name]
Senior Customer Service Representative
[Company Name]
